Founder of Maybach Music Group Rick Ross will be performing at this year’s Block Party. The American rapper who was here last year December with fellow American rapper Rich Homie Quan to give Mzansi audience an exclusive performance for their single collaborating with Spirit hitmaker Kwesta. He will be headlining the Durban festival at the Kings Park Stadium Outer Fields on 21 December, this is in partnership with Gagasi FM. The Dice Pineapple will also be performing the following day at Buffalo Park Stadium in East London.  Block Party has hosted big artists from and outside of Mzansi, the likes of Black Coffee once headlined at this annual party. Tickets for the Rick Ross Block Party are available at Web ticket prices starting from R345 and doors open at 2 pm. 